      This feature will install SCRM, a tool to model requirements
for scientific computing projects. The tool provides a meta-model
using EMF mechanisms and a graphical editor using GMF mechanisms.

Note: Installing this feature will install the required EMFCP and EMFStore features (version 0.7.3)
   </description>

